                     <interp inst="t17320906-16-person128" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . This is the original Will of 
               <persName id="t17320906-16-person129">
                  John 
                  Ward 
               <interp inst="t17320906-16-person129" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17320906-16-person129" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17320906-16-person129" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , I brought it from the Perogative-Office. I am Clerk to the Register. It has been pleaded in Behalf of one 
               <persName id="t17320906-16-person130">
                  James 
                  Lewis 
               <interp inst="t17320906-16-person130" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17320906-16-person130" type="given" value="James"></interp>
